- Smart layout: MWS-001 = demo mode, any other code = live Supabase mode
- PortalNav reads customer name from context for live customers
- Live portal at /p/[customerCode] with full Supabase data layer
- All pages consume from PortalDataContext (no direct demo imports)
- portal-data-context fetches from /api/agents/3pl-portal/all for live mode
